title: Bobby Flipped Off Everyone At The CMA's + Caitlin Got A CMA Shout-Out + Guess the ‘Mystery Guest’ + Lunchbox Pranks His Dad From Jail
itunes:title: Bobby Flipped Off Everyone At The CMA's + Caitlin Got A CMA Shout-Out + Guess the ‘Mystery Guest’ + Lunchbox Pranks His Dad From Jail
description:
Bobby gives us behind the scenes moments from the CMA Awards last night, including a bonehead moment. Bobby explains why he gave Caitlin a shout-out while he was presenting the award for 'Single Of The Year'. Plus, Bobby, Eddie and Lunchbox try to guess the mystery guest!
